title: The Organic Vegetarian Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Western, Take-out, Vietnamese
description: Tastefully appointed, comfortable, and clean restaurant. Most menu items are vegan but a few have dairy ingredients: Vietnamese cuisine, western style pasta, soups and porridge, hot pots. Has Wi-Fi. Dining on two floors, with room for large parties on both floors.
streetAddress: 54 Ly Van Phuc Stress, Tan Dinh Ward, District 1
